The following query can do the trick. We are using [$reduce][1] to replace space with a hyphen.
```
db.collection.aggregate([
	{
		$addFields:{
			&quot;slug&quot;:{
				$let:{
					&quot;vars&quot;:{
						&quot;array&quot;:{
							$split:[&quot;$title&quot;,&quot; &quot;]
						}
					},
					&quot;in&quot;:{
						$reduce:{
							&quot;input&quot;:&quot;$$array&quot;,
							&quot;initialValue&quot;:&quot;&quot;,
							&quot;in&quot;:{
								$concat:[&quot;$$value&quot;,&quot;-&quot;,&quot;$$this&quot;]
							}
						}
					}
				}
				
			}
		}
	},
	{
		$addFields:{
			&quot;slug&quot;:{
				$substr:[&quot;$slug&quot;,1,{ $strLenBytes: &quot;$slug&quot; }]
			}
		}
	}
]).pretty()
```

